responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "62EAD0944D97F14FAB58AB97668DE1C8", "Word has travelled faster than your boots could carry you. You met the face of the enemy with great vigor! Aye! A true survivor, but you must learn that you are but one soldier in the ranks of the Kaelar. ")
